appDesc.message: Lets you easily switch between multiple Vkontakte and other social networks accounts.

opts_3.message:
Additional information
This extension is based on cookies.
New profile is created using existing information, i.e. log into desired account first prior to creating new profile.
Refresh page after switching to another profile.

opts_14.message:
Hotkeys allows you to switch between extension tabs or pfofiles without mouse and calling popup window. Note, that these hotkeys can override almost all browser built-in hotkeys (e.g. switching betseen tabs on Ctrl+Tab or Ctrl+<tab number>).
Note. Changes will take effect on each browser tab after you refresh page.

opts_24.message: Save this text in any place and use for import.

opts_29.message: Merge imported profiles and settings with exciting

opts_30.message: Clear all exciting data and import new

opts_39.message: Automatically switch extension's active tab coresponding to browser's active tab's url

popup_6.message: Create new profile using current session information

help_1.message: Move mouse pointer to any element to see it's description

help_2.message: Tabs for switching between supported networks. In list are shown profiles for selected tab. Active tab highlighted with green color.

help_3.message: Create new profile using exciting browser cookies.

help_4.message: Profile sequence number, also used as profile identifier.

help_5.message: Profile's title. Active profile is marked as bold. Drag title to any another profile to switch profiles order.

help_6.message: Edit button. Click to change profile's title. Confirm by <Enter> or focus loss.

help_7.message: Remove button. Removes corresponding profile. This action can not be undone.
